      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity was selected for Ti-6Al-4V based on published tensile coupon data. A sensitivity study varying the tangent modulus ±20% showed less than 4% change in peak force QoI. Frictional contact (μ=0.3) between screw and rod was validated against a simplified sub-model with known analytical bounds."
