      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield strength (880 MPa), and UTS (950 MPa) for the Ti-6Al-4V rod were obtained from production-lot tensile coupons tested per ASTM E8. Screw geometry was captured by CMM with 5 μm resolution. Uncertainty in material inputs was propagated via Monte Carlo (n=1000) and found to contribute less than 2% to QoI variability."
