      "acceptanceCriteria": "Testing conducted under at least two distinct load levels or environmental conditions bracketing the COU operating range.",
      "rationale": "Testing was conducted under a single ASTM F1717 load configuration (static compression-bending at 5 mm/min crosshead rate, ambient temperature). No variation in load rate or temperature was explored. This limits the achievable level to Gradation 1, which is below the required Gradation 2 for this factor. The gap is noted as a limitation of the current validation dataset."
