      "rationale": "The ASTM F1717 fixture geometry was explicitly modeled as rigid analytical surfaces. Crosshead displacement was applied as a prescribed displacement boundary condition matching the experimental protocol. Fixture compliance was measured and incorporated as a corrective spring element, with less than 0.5% effect on reported stiffness."
